Package com.pandora.general.objects.services.abstractions.interfaces

Interface MapService

All Known Subinterfaces:
DischargesMapService, TerrestrialSourcesMapService, UpstreamSourcesMapService, VolumesMapService, YMapService
All Known Implementing Classes:
DischargesMapServiceImpl, TerrestrialSourcesMapServiceImpl, UpstreamSourcesMapServiceImpl, VolumesMapServiceImpl, YMapServiceImpl
public interface MapService
The MapService interface defines a common method for cleaning or resetting the map managed by the service. Implementations of this interface are expected to provide functionality for cleaning or resetting the internal map.

This interface is part of the abstraction layer for services related to managing maps.

0.0.1

      void cleanMap()
      Cleans or resets the map managed by the service.

      This method removes all entries from the map or performs any necessary cleanup operations to reset the state of the map.
